snippet.title: DRAGON BALL: THE BREAKERS – Season 6 Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
◤◢◤ Baby ◢◤◢ 
An "Infection-Type Raider" that hunts down survivors by infecting Civilians! 
Deceive and hunt down survivors to carry out the plan to turn the whole universe into Tuffles!
